snippet.title: 'No reason to doubt Pak, let's wait,' says Rajnath Singh on Pathankot

localized.description:
Amid uncertainty over talks with Pakistan after India made it clear that it wants action against those behind the Pathankot terror attack, Home Minister Rajnath Singh has indicated that Pakistan should be given more time.
